{"tid":1946160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"53萬人聯署促炒世衞總幹事","createTime":"2020-03-27T12:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T12:35:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa22852c14f3c3ed66256ef62e863ee2522e2505","tid":1946160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200327/7BDBJCP2KB7R7U3YD53ZIVOTKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2F7BDBJCP2KB7R7U3YD53ZIVOTKM%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=6fe04983\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2F7BDBJCP2KB7R7U3YD53ZIVOTKM%2F&h=b79e046d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200327/7BDBJCP2KB7R7U3YD53ZIVOTKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n53萬人聯署促炒世衞總幹事<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情全球確診宗數已逾46萬，世界衞生組織（WHO）總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）被指抗疫不力，網民發起聯署要求他辭職，至今已獲逾53萬人支持。<br />\n<br />\n在加拿大多倫多任髮型師的網民葉一森（Osuka Yip）<a href=\"http://於請願平台Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%96%BC%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0Change.org&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=8555168a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">於請願平台Change.org</a>發起聯署，頁面下以英、中、法、韓語等十多國語言寫出聲明，指摘譚德塞在1月23日不願宣佈在中國武漢爆發、無藥可治的新型冠狀病毒疫情為全球衞生緊急事件，確診病例及死亡人數在短時間暴增，「部份原因與譚德塞低估冠狀病毒有關」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200327/large/1585245968_8847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585245968_8847.jpg&h=d106e8f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未能保持政治中立<br />\n<br />\n聲明又說，譚德塞未經調查就全盤相信中國政府提供的死亡與病例數字，對他未能保持世衞政治中立感失望，不再適合擔任世衞秘書長，要求他立即辭職。聯署目標為100萬人，至今有超過53萬網民聯署，<a href=\"http://是Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%98%AFChange.org&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=efe35148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">是Change.org</a>同類聯署中最多人支持的一個。<br />\n<br />\n獲中國支持執掌世衞的譚德塞已非首次被指抗疫失責，2005年至2012年任祖國埃塞俄比亞衞生部長期間涉隱滿霍亂疫情，只稱之為「急性水瀉」。去年底外界初聞中國爆發不明疫情時，世衞在譚德塞領導下稱「沒確實證據顯示會人傳人」；即使台灣12月31日去信警告疫情會人傳人，世衞亦僅回應「收到了」；到1月27日終認錯，更正武漢肺炎在中國及全球擴散風險高，本月中將之定性為全球大流行疫症。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/加拿大Thinkpol網站"},{"pid":"9402215cb1fb15c41091df950d38380f06fb2541","tid":1946160,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲聯署對佢地到底有冇壓力？"},{"pid":"0e6616e15e6a6f996d0a20bbbe23b1c49a7d6673","tid":1946160,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9402215cb1fb15c41091df950d38380f06fb2541","tid":1946160,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲聯署對佢地到底有冇壓力？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"有,  <br />\n<br />\n乜都唔做就乜壓力都無"},{"pid":"fde8d891a915b6ddbc2778e2cc670e6f9152feb9","tid":1946160,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bbda530ae5069d47a7e2554c8fc35397653acf","tid":1946160,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9402215cb1fb15c41091df950d38380f06fb2541","tid":1946160,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲聯署對佢地到底有冇壓力？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"呢9個月以嚟你見過有幾多個聯署真係做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee16642ceb7e513e4a75b53eea68757f07cd7ece","tid":1946160,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"剩係炒咁小事，有冇得集體告到佢坐監"}]}